<LP>
   CLEVELAND -- Society Corp. said James W. Wert, a vice
chairman of this bank holding company, was named its chief
financial officer.
   Mr. Wert, 43 years old, succeeds Robert M. Patrick, 56,
senior vice president, who now is responsible for strategic
financial analysis.
</LP>
